<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify your email</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h2 style="color: #4f46e5;">Verify your email address</h2>
  <p>Hi {{fullName}},</p>
  <p>Thanks for signing up! Please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
  <p style="margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{verifyUrl}}" style="background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;">Verify email</a>
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">This link expires in 24 hours. If you didn't create an account, you can ignore this email.</p>
  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">Or copy this link: {{verifyUrl}}</p>
</body>
</html>
